    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "##AI in My Community: Helpful or Harmful?\r\n###Write Your Elevator Pitch\r\nNow that you’ve learned about how AI impacts your community, it’s time to share with others what you’ve discovered. \r\n\r\n\r\n###Do This\r\n1. Use **TaCoFoRT** to craft your prompt to AI Chat. Use it as a collaborator on your elevator pitch and remember you can use text, images, and documents to prompt it.\r\n2. Go back and forth with AI chat to make the best script you can.\r\n3. Make sure the pitch gets recorded in Part 3 of your Activity Guide.\r\n",
